==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Plumming
<hw>Plum"ming</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[See
<er>Plumb</er>.]</ety> <fld>(Min.)</fld> <def>The operation of finding,
by means of a mine dial, the place where to sink an air shaft, or to
bring an adit to the work, or to find which way the lode
inclines.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Plummy</ent>⟦br⟧
